videos.description: Michigan's Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman grabs the offensive rebound and finds Eli Brooks open for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Brooks knocks down 3-pointer

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson beats the shot clock and nails the finger-roll layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Simpson beats the buzzer with finger roll

videos.description: Ohio State's Kaleb Wesson grabs the offensive rebound and kicks it down low to Kyle Young for the layup.
videos.headline: Wesson's dime sets up Young for layup

videos.description: Michigan's Moritz Wagner gets the steal on the defensive end and finds Zavier Simpson in transition for the layup.
videos.headline: Wolverines defense sets up and-1 chance

videos.description: Michigan's Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman uses the screen and drives down the lane for the layup.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman sinks tough layup

videos.description: Michigan's Duncan Robinson finds Moritz Wagner off the pick-and-roll for the emphatic, two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Robinson finds Wagner for the slam

videos.description: Ohio State's Andrew Dakich finds Keita Bates-Diop at the top of the arc for the contested 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Bates-Diop earns chance for 5-point play

videos.description: Ohio State's Keita Bates-Diop pokes the ball loose to C.J. Jackson, who then finds Jae'Sean Tate open in transition for the dunk.
videos.headline: Tate throws down dunk after steal

videos.description: Ohio State's Kaleb Wesson gets the pass down low in the post and goes to work for the easy layup.
videos.headline: Wesson breaks out the post moves for the layup

videos.description: Ohio State brothers Andre Wesson and Kaleb Wesson deny Michigan down low to force a jump ball.
videos.headline: Double rejection from the Wesson brothers

videos.description: Ohio State's Jae'Sean Tate grabs the defensive rebound and goes all the way for the tough layup.
videos.headline: Tate goes coast to coast for and-1 opportunity

videos.description: Michigan's Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman leads Jordan Poole down the paint for the tough layup.
videos.headline: Poole converts and-1 chance

videos.description: After drawing the double team from Michigan defenders, Jae'Sean Tate kicks the ball out to Kam Williams for the open jumper.
videos.headline: Tate finds Williams for easy jumper
